name: 💫Positive Energy💫
description:
The essence of the story was actuslly magic mushrooms.Someone found those mushrooms and ate them.
He was happy to be in the forest.He had an interesting positive energy so when he ate the magic mushrooms, he started to see the things he like; cats, forest, sleeping... 

He only saw the cats while he was walking through the forest. Those cats were larger than human size, they were sleeping all the time. Colors were getting more brighter and sharper time to time; blue, purple, green and many more. He was dazzled by such bright world began to darken such a bit.
